        "subject": "LU-6202 utils: allow device_list for non-root users",
        "message": "LU-6202 utils: allow device_list for non-root users\n\nAllow /dev/obd to be opened by a non-root user.  If a read-write\nopen fails, try opening the device read-only.\n\nAllow ioctl(OBD_IOC_GETDEVICE) to be run by a non-root user.\n\nThe actual /dev/obd device is currently only accessible by root,\nbut if the permission is changed to allow non-root users, they\ncould use \"lctl dl\" to list the OBD devices without root access.\n\nSigned-off-by: Andreas Dilger <adilger@whamcloud.com>\nChange-Id: I928f38e6dd4949f7a9f5403c4d6ca372623ebbe5\n"
      },
